<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Handit.ai Alert</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 60px 40px;
        background: #ffffff url('cid:bg-image') no-repeat top center;
        background-size: cover;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        border-radius: 16px;
      }

      .logo {
        display: block;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        width: 180px;
        height: auto;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        color: #00272f !important;
      }

      .main-text {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #00272f !important;
        margin: 12px 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #02f7aa !important;
      }

      .details-box {
        background: rgba(2, 247, 170, 0.05);
        border-left: 4px solid #02f7aa;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }

      .details-box p {
        margin: 8px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #00272f !important;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        background-color: #02f7aa;
        color: #00272f !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-right: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background-color: #00d4aa;
      }

      .button-secondary {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #02f7aa !important;
        border: 2px solid #02f7aa;
      }

      .button-secondary:hover {
        background-color: rgba(2, 247, 170, 0.05);
      }

      .button-container {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .signature {
        margin-top: 32px;
        padding-top: 24px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 39, 47, 0.2);
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #00272f !important;
      }

      .signature-name {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #00272f !important;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .signature-title {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #00272f !important;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .signature-company {
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #02f7aa !important;
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .logo {
          width: 100px;
          margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .button {
          display: block;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
          text-align: center;
          margin-right: 0;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <img class="logo" src="cid:logo-image" alt="Handit.ai Logo" />
      
      <div class="greeting">
        Hello,
      </div>

      <p class="main-text">
        Handit has detected an issue with one of your AI models and is automatically working on a fix. 
        Here's what we found:
      </p>

      <div class="details-box">
        <p><span class="label">Agent:</span> {{agent_name}}</p>
        <p><span class="label">Node:</span> {{node_name}}</p>
        <p><span class="label">Issue Summary:</span><br />
          {{#each reviewer_summary}}
            <p>{{this}}</p><br />
          {{/each}}
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="main-text">
        Handit is currently analyzing this issue and will automatically implement a fix when ready. 
        You can review the full details and monitor the progress in your dashboard.
      </p>

      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="{{tracing_url}}" class="button">Review Details</a>
      </div>

      <p class="main-text">
        Our automated monitoring continuously watches your models to catch issues before they impact 
        your users and applies fixes automatically when possible.
      </p>

      <div class="signature">
        <div class="signature-name">â€” The Handit Team</div>
        <div class="signature-company">Handit.ai</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
